.DS_Store
*__pycache__*

# Rendered HTML belongs in _site/. Stray .html in the source tree are
# single-file `quarto render` artifacts — never commit them.
*.html

# team/index.qmd is generated by scripts/generate_team.py from the package
# registry (data/packages.yaml) and the member overlay (data/members/). It
# is committed so the site builds without network access; those data/ sources
# are the single source of truth.
